    "description": "Rising a Star is a relaxing horse care simulator game with immersive<strong> horsemanship tasks</strong> and management features. Your grandpa owns a stable which was the place one of the most important equestrian academies of Tuscany.  But now you're old enough to take care of it, and it's your turn to bring the academy to shine again.<br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141460/extras/5523370b61b21af45dd1c8a88ed37d9c.poster.avif?t=1695285666\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141460/extras/5523370b61b21af45dd1c8a88ed37d9c.webm?t=1695285666\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141460/extras/5523370b61b21af45dd1c8a88ed37d9c.mp4?t=1695285666\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Show Jumping Training</strong><br><br>You  can make some ShowJumping training with your horses, lvl up and partecipate at competitions.<br> <br>You have to jump all kind of obtacles like:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Verticals.<br></li><li>Oxers<br></li><li>Combinations<br></li><li>Water Jumps<br></li><li>Walls and more </li></ul><br><br><strong>Horsemanship Tasks</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141460/extras/b4d4038d9ae32b4e63df196d72f2eff3.poster.avif?t=1695285666\" width=618 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141460/extras/b4d4038d9ae32b4e63df196d72f2eff3.webm?t=1695285666\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141460/extras/b4d4038d9ae32b4e63df196d72f2eff3.mp4?t=16952856